---
import SiteLayout from '../layouts/site.astro';
---

<SiteLayout>
<main>
  <h1>devon.cash</h1>
  <p>The unfinished ruins of my personal projects.</p>

  <section>
    <hgroup>
      <h2>Music</h2>
    </hgroup>
    <ul>
      <li>
        <a href="https://churchladies.band">Church Ladies</a>
        <p>My band: blues/jazz/funk/whatever we want music.</p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <a href="https://corvmc.org">Corvallis Music Collective</a>
        <p>A local group dedicated to promoting music in Corvallis (I serve on the board).</p>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </section>
  <section>
    <hgroup>
      <h2>Tabletop Games</h2>
    </hgroup>
    <ul>
      <h3>Rulesets</h3>
      <li>
        <a href="/rulesets/by-word-and-deed">By Word and Deed</a>
        <p>A minimal RPG inspired by mythic storytelling.</p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <a href="/rulesets/descendants">Descendants</a>
        <p>A tactical RPG about humanity's will to survive in a galaxy of conflict and mystery.</p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <a href="/rulesets/pilgrimage">Pilgrimage</a>
        <p>A tabletop roleplaying game about finding your true self.</p>
      </li>
    </ul>
    <ul>
      <h3>Modules</h3>
      <li>
        <a href="/modules/luminous-order">The Luminous Order</a>
        <p>A module for space-faring dungeons and dragons inspired by Destiny</p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <a href="/modules/lancer-hardsuits">LANCER: Hardsuits</a>
        <p>Enhanced pilot hardsuits for use in the Lancer TTRPG, inspired by Titanfall.</p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <a href="/modules/lancer-scarcity">LANCER: Scarcity</a>
        <p>A rules module for LANCER offering guidance on operations without easy access to printers.</p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <a href="/modules/wwn-eberron">Worlds Without Number: Eberron</a>
        <p>A conversion of the Eberron setting for use with Worlds Without Number.</p>
      </li>
    </ul>
    <ul>
      <h3>Tools</h3>
      <li>
        <a href="https://intmatrix.net">The Intelligence Matrix</a>
        <p>A set of table-based generators for use in FIST.</p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <a href="/tools/knave-character-generator">Knave Character Generator</a>
        <p>A simple character generator for the Knave RPG.</p>
      </li>
    </ul>
</section>

</main>
</SiteLayout>

<style>
main {
  max-width: 1024px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 1em;
}

main section {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
  grid-template-rows: repeat(auto-fit, auto);
  gap: 1em;
  margin: 2em 0;
}

h3 {
  margin-bottom: .5em;
}

li {
	margin-left: 1.5em;
  margin-bottom: .5em;
}

section hgroup {
	grid-column: 1 / -1;
}
</style>